description:
What modern-day system is represented by the whore of Babylon in Revelation 17? Who is the woman called “Mystery Babylon”? This verse-by-verse exposé of Revelation 17 describes a woman controlling a coalition of powers. The woman has the attributes of the mystery religion of Babylon and entices the world to follow her precepts.

Who were the Gnostics? How are secret societies connected? What is the origin of sports and the Olympics? Find out how these things are related to the whore of Babylon as Walter Veith presents a thorough exegesis of Revelation 17 and identifies Babylon’s influence on modern religion and society. Discover how Revelation 17 sets the stage for the final events in the conflict between good and evil.


Click here to download the Study Guide for this lecture: http://pdf.amazingdiscoveries.org/Study_Guides/TO/TO220-A_Woman_Rides_The_Beast.pdf
